		attributions: [
			'Developed and maintained Digital Products using NestJS, Docker, and Azure Pipelines, contributing to product reliability and deployment efficiency.',
			'Contributed to the design and implementation of monitoring solutions, including alerts and dashboards for application health and team metrics, enhancing system observability.',
